00:57:39,843 --> 00:57:40,943
<font color=#FFFF00>Kantor ini sangat mengagumkan.</font>

722
00:57:45,343 --> 00:57:48,983
<font color=#FFFF00>(1 tahun kemudian)</font>

723
00:58:05,633 --> 00:58:08,973
<font color=#FFFF00>(Almarhum Lee Sung Hoon)</font>

724
00:58:10,303 --> 00:58:14,603
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa Ahjussi bahagia di atas surga sana ?</font>

725
00:58:17,073 --> 00:58:19,043
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibuku juga di sana.</font>

726
00:58:22,513 --> 00:58:23,713
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi...</font>

727
00:58:24,653 --> 00:58:27,923
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bisa melihat Ahjussi dari Sosok Paman Sung Joon ...</font>

728
00:58:28,023 --> 00:58:29,823
<font color=#FFFF00>setiap hari,</font>

729
00:58:31,453 --> 00:58:35,393
<font color=#FFFF00>tapi terkadang aku masih merindukanmu.</font>

730
00:58:44,773 --> 00:58:46,473
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau sedang menyapanya?</font>

731
00:58:47,343 --> 00:58:48,403
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya .</font>

732
00:58:54,443 --> 00:58:55,913
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini aku, Sung Hoon.</font>

733
00:58:59,753 --> 00:59:00,853
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku baik-baik saja sekarang.</font>

734
00:59:05,493 --> 00:59:07,093
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf karena tidak bisa menepati janjiku.</font>

735
00:59:12,533 --> 00:59:14,503
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku meninggalkanmu sendirian lagi.</font>

736
00:59:16,433 --> 00:59:18,003
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku, Sung Hoon.</font>

737
00:59:25,683 --> 00:59:27,683
<font color=#FFFF00>(Mendiang Lee Sung Hoon)</font>

738
00:59:50,033 --> 00:59:51,703
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau masih bingung ...</font>

739
00:59:52,643 --> 00:59:56,213
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa kau dan bagaimana kau harus menjalani hidupmu?</font>

740
00:59:58,013 --> 00:59:59,083
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

741
00:59:59,743 --> 01:00:01,683
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak ingin memikirkan hal itu lagi.</font>

742
01:00:02,853 --> 01:00:04,813
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa aku harus terus menjalani hidupku.</font>

743
01:00:06,083 --> 01:00:07,923
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin membantu orang lain sebisaku ...</font>

744
01:00:08,283 --> 01:00:10,053
<font color=#FFFF00>dan aku akan menerima bantuan ketika aku membutuhkannya.</font>

745
01:00:11,293 --> 01:00:12,963
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah begitu kehidupan orang normal?</font>

746
01:00:14,423 --> 01:00:16,793
<font color=#FFFF00>Yahh, Kau sudah dewasa sekarang.</font>

747
01:00:17,093 --> 01:00:18,663
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau seperti seorang manusia sekarang.</font>

748
01:00:40,183 --> 01:00:42,023
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kau lakukan, Paman Sung Joon?</font>

749
01:00:42,253 --> 01:00:43,853
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku merasakan angin.</font>

750
01:00:45,823 --> 01:00:47,393
<font color=#FFFF00>Soo Yeon, apa kau mau mencobanya?</font>

751
01:00:47,993 --> 01:00:48,993
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

